OL,3,CMetal detectorist reunites First World
OL,4,CWar brooch with family
OL,6,FJohn Bradbury found a sweetheart
OL,7,Fbrooch bearing the name "Jane" during
OL,8,Fa search of the countryside as Jahmal
OL,9,FWilliams-Thomas reports.
OL,11,FA metal detectorist has reunited a
OL,12,Ffamily with a First World War love
OL,13,Ftoken thought to have been lost while
OL,14,Fthe owner was 'tending to the cows'.
OL,16,FJohn Bradbury discovered the
OL,17,Fsweetheart brooch during a search of
OL,18,Ffarmland in the countryside close to
OL,19,Fhis home in Brierfield, East
OL,20,FLancashire, in 2023.
