OL,3,CMetal detectorist reunites First World
OL,4,CWar brooch with family
OL,6,FHe immediately knew the silver pin was
OL,7,Fa sentimental treasure when he noticed
OL,8,Fit was embossed with the name 'Jane'.
OL,10,FNow he has finally been able to give
OL,11,Fthe heirloom back to the family of its
OL,12,Fowner.
OL,14,FA keen metal detectorist, John had
OL,15,Ffound many interesting things over the
OL,16,Fyears including many First World War
OL,17,Fartefacts and coins.
