OL,4,CWar brooch with family
OL,6,F"It was just a normal day for me", he
OL,7,Fsaid. "I had found all sorts of things
OL,8,Fwhen I suddenly got a high reading on
OL,9,Fmy machine.
OL,11,F"I was in shock. I bent down and found
OL,12,Fthe brooch with the name "Jane" on it.
OL,14,F"I told my friend about it and he said
OL,15,F- you know what you've got there -
OL,16,Fit's a World War One sweetheart
OL,17,Fbrooch. Now we just need to find the
OL,18,Ffamily!"
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
