OL,4,CWar brooch with family
OL,6,FJohn tracked down the previous owners
OL,7,Fof the farmland to The Shooter's Arms
OL,8,FPub, near Burnley, and discovered the
OL,9,Fbrooch had belonged to Jane Cannon.
OL,11,FJane was gifted the sweetheart brooch
OL,12,Fby her husband, Arthur, in 1915.
OL,14,FHer great niece Lucy Nicholson was
OL,15,Fdelighted and shocked when she heard
OL,16,Fit had been found.
OL,18,F"Jane's sweetheart Arthur, who she
OL,19,Fwent on to marry, would have given her
OL,20,Fthe pin", she said.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
