OL,6,FThey were bought and presented by the
OL,7,Fserviceman as they left for war.
OL,9,F"It's amazing it has been found in
OL,10,Fsuch good condition," Lucy added.
OL,11,F"Especially with the cows up there who
OL,12,Fhave been trampling around over the
OL,13,Fyears."
